  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective cohort study investigating cardiac function and cardiac biomarkers in
      patients with acute Aneurysmal Subarachnoid Haemorrhage (aSAH). The aims of the study are to
      document the incidence of myocardial dysfunction,to find the predictive factors of
      myocardial dysfunction, describe heart rate variability and to assess the impact of all
      cardiac problems on morbidity and mortality.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
